              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36916981/" class="">孔子在中国与世界历史的形象</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/" class=" " title="公益霎哈嘉瑜伽">公益霎哈嘉瑜伽</a>
